All Possible Pools 
The maxiumum items you can query at once is 1000. Thus to get all possible pools, you can interate using the skip variable. To get pools beyond the
first 1000 you can also set the skip as shown below .
Skipping First 1000 Pools 
This query sets the skip value and returns the first 10 responses after the first 1000.
{
  pools(first:10, skip:1000){
    id
    token0 {
      id
      symbol
    }
    token1 {
      id
      symbol
    }
  }
}
