All pairs in Uniswap  
The Graph limits entity return amounts to 1000 per query as of now . To get all pairs on Uniswap use a loop and graphql skip
query to fetch multiple chunks of 1000 pairs. The query would look like this (where skip is some incrementing variable
passed into your query).
{
 query pairs($skip: Int!) {
   pairs(first: 1000, skip: $skip) {
     id
   }
 }
}
